In [52]:
def is_outlier(adata, metric: str, nmads: int):
    outlier = (
        (adata.obs[metric] > np.median(adata.obs[metric]) + nmads * median_abs_deviation(adata.obs[metric]))
        | (adata.obs[metric] < np.median(adata.obs[metric]) - nmads * median_abs_deviation(adata.obs[metric]))
    )
    return outlier
